rmissions":{"admin":false,"maintain":false,"push":false,"triage":false,"pull":true}},"body":"Same ticket https://github.com/yiisoft/yii2/issues/3601\n\nAfter refresh captcha, the validator is always return an error.\nReproduced if using the route module 'main'.\n\n1) I tired:\n\n```\n<?= $form->field($model, 'verifyCode')->widget(Captcha::className(), [\n        'captchaAction' => 'activate-card/captcha'\n    ])  ?>\n```\n\nrules:\n`['verifyCode', 'captcha', 'captchaAction' => 'main/activate-card/captcha'],\n` \nresult:\njs captha settings:\n`{\"refreshUrl\":\"/main/activate-card/captcha?refresh=1\",\"hashKey\":\"yiiCaptcha/activate-card/captcha\"});`\nvalidator option hashKey:\n`yiiCaptcha/main/activate-card/captcha`\n\n $('body').data(options.hashKey); in yii.validation.js not same with $('body').data(settings.hashKey, [data.hash1, data.hash2]); in yii.captha.js\n\n2) I tried to specify the full path\n\n```\n<?= $form->field($model, 'verifyCode')->widget(Captcha::className(), [\n        'captchaAction' => 'main/activate-card/captcha'\n    ])  ?>\n\n```\n\nresult:\nImage not found. Url: /main/main/activate-card/captcha?v=56f327fe35936\njs captha settings:\n`{\"refreshUrl\":\"/main/main/activate-card/captcha?refresh=1\",\"hashKey\":\"yiiCaptcha/main/activate-card/captcha\"}`\n\n3) If set path with / still not working\n\n```\n<?= $form->field($model, 'verifyCode')->widget(Captcha::className(), [\n        'captchaAction' => '/main/activate-card/captcha'\n    ])  ?>\n\n```\n\nresult:\n{\"refreshUrl\":\"/main/activate-card/captcha?refresh=1\",\"hashKey\":\"yiiCaptcha//main/activate-card/captcha\"}\nJust get an error...\n\n4). If you set captchaAction  'activate-card/captcha' in the model rules is getting the error 500.\n\nIn my case, it helped fix:\nClass yii\\captcha\\Captcha https://github.com/yiisoft/yii2/blob/master/framework/captcha/Captcha.php#L153\n\n```\n142:    protected function getClientOptions()\n153: -            'hashKey' => \"yiiCaptcha/{$route[0]}\",\n153: +             'hashKey' => \"yiiCaptcha\".Url::toRoute($this->captchaAction),\n```\n\n| Q | A |\n| --- | --- |\n| Yii version | 2.0.7 |\n| PHP version | 5.5.9 |\n| Operating system | Ubuntu 14.04 |\n","reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/yiisoft/yii2/issues/11181/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"timeline_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/yiisoft/yii2/issues/11181/timeline","performed_via_github_app":null,"state_reason":"completed"}},"event":"cross-referenced"}]